[620.753755, "o", "\r\n================================================================================\r\nTASK COMPLETION REPORT\r\n================================================================================\r\n\r\nOBJECTIVE ACHIEVED:\r\n✓ Compiled pyknotid Cython extensions (chelpers, ccomplexity, cinvariants)\r\n✓ Fixed Numpy 2.3.0 compatibility issues\r\n✓ Installed pyknotid to system's global Python environment\r\n✓ README example code runs successfully without errors\r\n✓ Core tests pass (test_spacecurve.py: 16/16, test_knot.py: 2/2)\r\n\r\nMINIMAL STATE CHANGES:\r\n\r\n1. REPOSITORY CLONED:\r\n   Location: /app/pyknotid\r\n   Source: github.com/SPOCKnots/pyknotid.git (tag 0.5.3)\r\n\r\n2. SOURCE FILES MODIFIED (8 files for compatibility):\r\n   - pyknotid/invariants.py (numpy type aliases)\r\n   - pyknotid/make/periodic_knot.py (numpy type aliases)\r\n   - pyknotid/make/torus.py (gcd import fix)\r\n   - pyknotid/representations/dtnotation.py (numpy type aliases)\r\n   - pyknotid/representations/representation.py (numpy type aliases)\r\n   - pyknotid/spa"]
[620.753883, "o", "cecurves/knot.py (numpy type aliases)\r\n   - pyknotid/spacecurves/openknot.py (numpy type aliases)\r\n   - pyknotid/spacecurves/spacecurve.py (numpy type aliases)\r\n\r\n3. COMPILED EXTENSIONS CREATED (4 .so files):\r\n   - pyknotid/spacecurves/chelpers.cpython-313-x86_64-linux-gnu.so\r\n   - pyknotid/spacecurves/ccomplexity.cpython-313-x86_64-linux-gnu.so\r\n   - pyknotid/cinvariants.cpython-313-x86_64-linux-gnu.so\r\n   - pyknotid/simplify/coctree.cpython-313-x86_64-linux-gnu.so\r\n\r\n4. BUILD ARTIFACTS (standard, expected):\r\n   - build/ directory (C compilation artifacts)\r\n   - pyknotid.egg-info/ directory (package metadata)\r\n\r\n5. GLOBAL INSTALLATION:\r\n   - Package: pyknotid 0.5.3\r\n   - Location: /usr/local/lib/python3.13/site-packages (editable)\r\n   - Source: /app/pyknotid\r\n\r\nCOMPATIBILITY FIXES APPLIED:\r\n- Python 3.13: Changed 'from fractions import gcd' to 'from math import gcd'\r\n- Numpy 2.0+: Replaced deprecated type aliases:\r\n  * n.float → n.float64\r\n  * n.int → n.intp\r\n  * n.complex → n.complex128\r\n\r\nVERIFICATIO"]
